headline: FIS to Report Second Quarter Earnings on August 5, 2025
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., July 16, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial services technology, will announce second quarter 2025 financial results on Tues., August 5, 2025, prior to market open.

headline: Why Fidelity National (FIS) Could Beat Earnings Estimates Again

headline: FIS Recognized by CNBC as One of the World’s Top Fintech Companies
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., July 16, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced that it has once again been recognized on CNBC’s World’s Top Fintech Companies list, in the Enterprise Fintech category. 2025 marks the third year in a row that FIS has earned a spot on the annual global ranking, developed in partnership with market research firm Statista.
